headline.print_headline: Chicago Marathon Champion Jeptoo Fails Doping Test
headline.main: Chicago Marathon Champion Jeptoo Fails Doping Test

lead_paragraph: Leading female marathoner Rita Jeptoo of Kenya failed a doping test a few weeks before winning her second consecutive Chicago Marathon, her agent and national federation said Friday.
